{"tid":981324,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)霸王花1 3 A計劃1-2 空中監獄","createTime":"2019-01-14T08:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T18:10:24.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0cc09d5850810047d7f5c949f4303520285e78","tid":981324,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=6IUnvXXzGGBLGTx%2BbciszpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b0295734\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=6IUnvXXzGGBLGTx%2BbciszpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=26161aad\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=6IUnvXXzGGBLGTx%2BbciszpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=4b2d0130\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://photo1.9you.com/pic/userphoto/55/45/2037185545/lxvt1219314691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphoto1.9you.com%2Fpic%2Fuserphoto%2F55%2F45%2F2037185545%2Flxvt1219314691.jpg&h=eb8a1393&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/40/Project_A_film_poster_(Original_Hong_Kong_Version).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F40%2FProject_A_film_poster_%28Original_Hong_Kong_Version%29.jpg&h=343ee6da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1d/Conairinternational.jpg/220px-Conairinternational.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F1%2F1d%2FConairinternational.jpg%2F220px-Conairinternational.jpg&h=c2fc6b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.香港以前本來沒有女子特警隊，但受到女警司Madam胡（胡慧中 飾）的出色表現，令到警局高層決定以她爲班底，組建有史以來第一支女子特&shy;警隊&mdash;&mdash;「霸王花」，而Madam胡就被委任為「霸王花」的隊長兼教官，負責訓練和指揮每一個「霸王花」隊員，進行與飛虎隊一樣的嚴格訓練。在幾個月的嚴格訓練下，「霸王花」很快就能出動執行任務了<br />\n<br />\n2.警方臥底在一次軍火交易中被殺，為查真相，胡警司決派霸王花調查，由簡Sir負責指揮。<br />\n簡Sir對眾女存有偏見，欲以嚴峻訓練，迫走各人，反被戲弄，最後，互相諒解，同登賭船查案。<br />\n適時，美、日、台、港四大幫會為爭奪波蘭新賭場地盤，將在船上舉行一場賭王爭霸戰，船東已選定賭王出戰，其他幫會亦各派先鋒上船，一探虛實<br />\n<br />\n3.香港開埠初期，海盜橫行，在香港的海面，盜魁羅三炮與奸商周永齡互相勾結，深悉貨運情報，因而無往不利，官府亦為之束手。水警沙展馬如龍對官府政策非常不滿，憤而辭職，與卓一飛合謀對付海盜，卓一飛雖然武功高強，可惜他唯利是圖，他與馬如龍合作騙取軍火，旨在從中圖利。羅三炮勢力龐大，馬如龍和卓一飛二人屢剿失利。馬如龍心有不甘，重新加入水師警隊，與上司洪天賜、卓一飛三人合力喬裝闖入匪巢，終於將海盜一網打盡。<br />\n<br />\n4.清朝末年的香港，在上、中、西環有「鎮三環」之稱的幫辦暗中勾結西環惡霸勾心虎，西環治安一時烏煙瘴氣。警官馬如龍（成龍）奉命接管西環後，迅速將勾心虎拘捕人獄，招來「鎮三環」的怨恨。 彼時內地革命風雲翻湧，革命黨人來港宣傳，併計劃營救被捕同志。為將革命黨人一網打盡，清廷派遣密使聯絡鎮三環，馬如龍結識白影紅、瑩瑩、珊珊等革命黨人（張曼玉、關之琳、劉嘉玲等）後也被捲入鬥爭漩渦，而同時，一群四肢發達頭腦簡單的海盜正在伺機向馬如龍報仇.......<br />\n<br />\n5.八年前，自海軍陸戰隊受訓完畢的卡麥倫坡（尼可拉斯凱吉飾）為了保護剛懷孕的妻子免於小混混的騷擾，導致過失殺人被判了十年徒刑。<br />\n在獄中表現良好的他，終於在女兒八歲生日當天獲得假釋，卡麥倫坡希望能親自將生日禮物送到女兒手中，因此要求典獄官讓他登上空中監獄，以節省舟車往返的時間。 但這踏空中監獄正巧搭載一批全美最殘暴兇狠的犯人....<br />\n<br />\n4 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=6IUnvXXzGGBLGTx%2BbciszpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=55f81a38\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=6IUnvXXzGGBLGTx%2BbciszpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e3c16085\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f9cb1c0bc8f11d9635ebf437fc9f9a3a21418f","tid":981324,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e672db11d4c5ac3ae95f44bc55a8848ba959de43","tid":981324,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0e99c4aa529d6cb217e0675582aa8fc211b20a","tid":981324,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc65c14697ecfbb19ccddaf6c0ccc1f9d8ef1c6d","tid":981324,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427229e21ac865b3b4bf00e2a7d17d041b5656e0","tid":981324,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709d5c250a491ab47db44e8f0a4aa13e7b12ed6c","tid":981324,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:18:54.000Z","msg"